178
00:10:13,440 --> 00:10:14,170
So forget it.

179
00:10:14,720 --> 00:10:15,150
But...

180
00:10:16,610 --> 00:10:17,470
Your Highness.

181
00:10:17,990 --> 00:10:18,880
Don't you think

182
00:10:19,360 --> 00:10:22,270
you should have talked to me about such a big deal?

183
00:10:23,880 --> 00:10:25,010
What's there to say?

184
00:10:25,640 --> 00:10:28,040
It didn't work out. Why should I talk to you?

185
00:10:29,160 --> 00:10:29,620
You just

186
00:10:30,430 --> 00:10:32,560
mind your own business in the mansion.

187
00:10:35,100 --> 00:10:35,940
Lord ordered

188
00:10:36,920 --> 00:10:38,250
