858
00:41:28,320 --> 00:41:29,850
We've indeed harvested a lot.

859
00:41:29,850 --> 00:41:30,360
Yes.

860
00:41:30,470 --> 00:41:31,720
Now the problem of our meals

861
00:41:31,720 --> 00:41:32,880
