862
00:41:32,910 --> 00:41:33,180
Yes.

863
00:41:35,910 --> 00:41:36,510
All right.

864
00:41:39,480 --> 00:41:41,060
Take this to Hao Jia.

865
00:41:42,750 --> 00:41:44,010
This is for Shangguan.

866
00:41:44,600 --> 00:41:45,530
This is for Sisi.

867
00:41:46,130 --> 00:41:47,800
This is for Haitang.

868
00:41:49,360 --> 00:41:50,420
This is for Song Wu.

869
00:41:50,690 --> 00:41:52,400
