870
00:41:52,600 --> 00:41:53,730
Remember to tell her

871
00:41:53,740 --> 00:41:55,050
that the harvest is not good.

872
00:41:55,050 --> 00:41:56,250
Ask her to forgive me.

873
00:41:59,560 --> 00:42:00,090
