889
00:42:55,760 --> 00:42:56,420
It's okay.

890
00:42:56,800 --> 00:42:57,820
Please eat.

891
00:42:58,230 --> 00:42:59,430
Don't worry about us.

892
00:43:02,560 --> 00:43:04,440
